{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, long-term sea-level data is mandatory for predictive research.",
    "Nevertheless, obtaining such data can be challenging due to the high cost of monitoring [45].",
    "When extended sea-level measurements are unavailable, ML methods present a feasible alternative, as they necessitate shorter time periods.",
    "In recent years, numerous ML applications have emerged for predicting both short-and long-term sea-level changes using TG data.",
    "Researchers have explored the use of lagged sea-level measurements and meteorological factors for this purpose."
  ]
}